{"tid":2075888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年遭警暴 重抑鬱免差館報到","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T07:09:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9bc6bdaeb6d295f0e1220aacfd8149ffcfde82","tid":2075888,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/TWUXEI7EZWH5572MCJ6LY46N4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FTWUXEI7EZWH5572MCJ6LY46N4Y%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7ojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=c9736c6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FTWUXEI7EZWH5572MCJ6LY46N4Y%2F&h=c848f981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200623/TWUXEI7EZWH5572MCJ6LY46N4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n少年遭警暴 重抑鬱免差館報到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXJ62NFPW7N43XEXKYK2PAKRQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXJ62NFPW7N43XEXKYK2PAKRQQ.jpg&h=b2c89840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名17歲男生被捕後遇警暴，患上嚴重抑鬱及創傷後壓力症候群，獲准保釋期間不用往警署報到。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【拒捕案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民去年10月發起「神獸罷鷲」行動，引發激烈警民衝突，一名17歲男生在旺角被防暴警捉着，大喊在場人士幫手，有人起飛腳將防暴警踢跌及有人追打。17歲男生最終被捕獲，事隔九個月後被控拒捕，昨提堂。辯方投訴指男生被防暴警用盾壓地致昏厥，在警車上遭毆打全身及下體，事後患上嚴重抑鬱及創傷後壓力症候群，害怕面對警員及前往警署。署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀最終批准男生保釋期間不用到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n17歲陳姓男學生。。。。。件7月20日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方不反對被告保釋，但要求法庭施加嚴苛保釋條件，包括定期向警署報到、離港禁令等。辯方表示，陳願遵守離港禁令及宵禁令，但不願往警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n將和本案合併的另。。。。。武器等三罪。<br />\n<br />\n兩人均非網上瘋傳影片中的起飛腳男子。謝還柙至今已逾九個月，昨申請保釋再被拒。甘則於去年10月17日獲准保釋候訊，其後潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三學生獲撤控准簽保<br />\n<br />\n此外，三名學生去年。。。。。姓女學生。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC1492/20<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n、2546/19、691/20"},{"pid":"08f0e7c057110dec0109138c0769d3675b335bc6","tid":2075888,"uid":282352,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去登記一萬蚊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c7c13215bb6f3485b403e378fa1219abfe5386","tid":2075888,"uid":50526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"#2 blocked"},{"pid":"0cc4fddb1a5b96978a4e4ee36d04efa3080a50fd","tid":2075888,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"Cls 又一個垃圾官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}